let Categories = [
   'Movies',
   'Music',
   'Technology',
   'Sports',
   'Fashion',
   'Health',
   'Travel',
   'Entertainment',
   'Gaming',
   'Education',
   'Poem'
];
export const categories = Categories.sort();
